---

This model wraps ESMStabP, a protein thermostability (Tm) predictor by
Marcus Ramos, Robert L. Jernigan, and Mesih Kilinc
(https://github.com/marcusramos2024/ESMStabP). ESMStabP builds on ESM-2
embeddings (Meta AI / FAIR, MIT License).

NOTE TO MAINTAINERS: The upstream ESMStabP repository does not currently ship a
LICENSE file, so the copyright holder and year above are a best-effort
attribution to the repository owner / lead author (paper year 2025). Confirm the
intended license and copyright line with the authors before public release.
